Details
Fred Winkler Art and Sabby teamed up with Fisty &Darc once again to bring you this exciting and very special release

Introducing FWSA Vanessa, a sexy young character for Victoria 7 and her jewelry for Genesis 3 Female(s)

The head, body and ears for Vanessa are uniquely custom sculpted in Zbrush, and the skin was created using high quality photo references for depth and detail. She also comes with custom sculpted square nails as well as longer upper lashes that can be dialed to your desired length. Furthermore there are custom nipples that will apply when the main morph dials are applied.

There is also a Sexy Lips expression included that can be applied via the library or using the specially created dial.

The Vanessa Jewellery was designed with Vanessa in mind, but also had loads of fits and adjustments giving all your Genesis 3 Female(s) a great and stunning look.

Please Note: While Vanessa and her jewelry were designed with Daz Studio 4.8 in mind, and its amazing Iray render engine, she will also work and look great using the 3Delight render engine!

ReadMe: The nails remove option in the MATs folders, will also remove the long nail morph.
